Enable tap to (left) click and two finger tap to right click on Debian 8.6.0 x64 LXDE

leafpad /home/andrej/.config/lxsession/LXDE/autostart

add there these lines:

@synclient TapButton1=1
@synclient tapbutton2=3

The first command enables tap to click, and the other two finger tap to right click.
The changes take effect after reboot.

sources:
https://www.reddit.com/r/linux/comments/3cy47r/enabling_two_finger_tap_right_click_kali/